338
00:24:41.785 --> 00:24:43.220
Sei su <i>Street Talk</i>.

339
00:24:43.301 --> 00:24:44.902
<i>Salve, sig.na Stratten,</i>
<i>Mi chiamo George</i>.


340
00:24:44.903 --> 00:24:46.158
