1513
01:26:15.438 --> 01:26:16.815
Non significava niente per me.

1514
01:26:17.439 --> 01:26:18.540
Segnale.

1515
01:26:19.241 --> 01:26:20.442
Dorothy?

1516
01:26:21.884 --> 01:26:22.944
Sam, sono qui.

